Operation Context:
	- Operation Context tells Run method of the current execution context like start time, end time, resource details etc.
	- Class:
	public class OperationContext<TResource> where TResource : IResource
	    {
	        public TResource Resource;
	        public string StartTime;  // UTC
	        public string EndTime; // UTC
	        public bool IsInternalCall { get; private set; } // sets to false when detector is called from azure portal, true for applens
	        public string RequestId;
	        public Dictionary<string, string> QueryParams;
	        public ILogger Logger;
	    }

	- The declaration of OperationContext is is different based on the following:
